          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "打一口吃一口又香又甜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "吃饭后再吃烟钟敲三点。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "住了宿夜间事不比细言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "从此后不回家住了半年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "果然能鬼推磨话不虚传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "卖房产当衣服拆变坟田。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可恨她又对我巧语花言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "将女人租出去离了家园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "烦中人却将他送入科班。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "也是我祖有德学了花脸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "学的是《打龙袍》、《打銮驾》、《铡美案》、《锁五龙》、《御果园》、"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "《牧虎关》、《二进宫》、《捉放曹》，还有一出《绑子上殿》，还学得《雅观"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "楼》、《白良关》、《白虎堂》，还有八本《铡判官》。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多说道气死傻奎好比谭三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一日两两日三钱又花完。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不能见妻和子怎回家园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "浑身上如水浇举步维艰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "挑一分吃几口才得舒展。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听谯楼三更鼓漏尽声残。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡松亭睡。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魏不饱 （内二黄导板） 驾起了羊角风团团乱转，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鬼卒、魏不饱同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魏不饱 （回龙） 尊一声众爷台细听我言："
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叹世人受苦情却把谁怨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到如今后悔迟也是枉然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄垛板",
          "musical_style": "二黄垛板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "人生来当忘八、当兔子、大茶壶、扛叉杆、跑局场，人人可干，"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "万不可装公子学吃大烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "吃烟人万不能福寿绵延。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "如骂他就如骂令尊一般。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪知道所劝的金石良言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "迎接了胡大哥一同上天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你自顾吃大烟自觉好看"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好朋友把此事将人解劝"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "懵懂人他必然以此为怨"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫鬼卒快引我把故友相见"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄倒板",
          "musical_style": "二黄倒板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "梦魂中见贤弟面前立站，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（火彩。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我看你宛如那在生一般。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到如今我在阳你在阴间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "是、是、是何故快快地细说一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "曾记得那时节同往烟馆"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你今到此有何公干"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "尊一声胡大哥且免悲叹，"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听小弟将来由表一表根源："
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "玉帝说吃烟人死后升天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "此等事若不干枉在世间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "上了天那好处一目了然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "阎王爷注生死自有循环。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "自古来大圣贤也赴阴间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你须将红尘事隔在一边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今日里遵玉旨将你来看"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到阴司不治罪仍住烟馆"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "劝大哥休害怕切莫惊战"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你休要想不开脱离此难"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "南北斗注上册早已定限"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏不饱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "及早地随小弟天宫回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "闻此言唬得我浑身打战，"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "三魂渺七魄茫毛骨悚然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你又说人生死自有循环。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大丈夫生和死有甚为难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "年深久免不得尸骨不全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的妻啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今日里遵玉旨将你来看"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到阴司不治罪仍住烟馆"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "劝大哥休害怕切莫惊战"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你休要想不开脱离此难"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "南北斗注上册早已定限"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "及早地随小弟天宫回转"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你母子在阳世我在阴间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "只怨我不学好爱吃洋烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "劝世人休把那洋烟来玩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑院子醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫一声小肥鹿细听我言。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑院子允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你快找我妻子与我见面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你、你、你就说我的命万难保全。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑院子允，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "顿然间神恍惚浑身打战，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡松亭吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡松亭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "无常到万事休命归阴间。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡松亭死。魏不饱、鬼卒引胡松亭同下。）"
        }
      ],
